1. Install apache2 and wsgi module.
    Using zypper(rpm) or build from source. Devel package of apache2 and apache2-worker is neccessary.

2. Install pip for python.

3. Using pip install xxx(name)==xxx(version) to install corresponding python lib.

4. Configure wsgi.conf in apache2.       eg. corn.d/wsgi.conf

5. Configure the wsgi file for project.  eg. django.wsgi
